mb|2S|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Many would not open 2@S because they won't open a weak 2 with an outside 4 card major. Despite what other teachers tell you that is really a wrong reason. Most likely when you have a 6-card suit, that is where you want to play it. |
