nt|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Further, a preempt is meant to be a destructive bid against the opponents not a constructive bid. You are taking a calculated risk (which often works well) that making it hard for the opponents is to your advantage. You are not worrying about precise bidding. |
