nt|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Another reason that some won't open East's had a weak 2 is that East only has 4 HCP and theoretically a weak 2 shows 5-10. However, there are at least 2 good reasons why a weak 2 by East is still correct.|
