nt|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|a) East is at favorable vulnerability (their side not vul, the opponents vul). That is an ideal time to preempt and you should strain to do so, even stretching if necessary.|
